table
  thead
    tr
      th width="100" Kundennummer
      th Name / Firma
      th width="120" Kategorie
      th Tags
      th.text-right width="100" Aktionen

  tbody
    - @contacts.each do |contact|
      = render partial: "contacts/index/item_contact", locals: { contact: contact }

  tfoot
    tr
      td class="text-right" colspan=5
        h4
          span.bold = @contacts.count
          span.thin Kontakte gefunden